                            <comment id="26408" author="yong.fan" created="Wed, 11 Jan 2012 20:32:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ticket for Lustre manual updating is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-33&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-33&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="26404" author="cliffw" created="Wed, 11 Jan 2012 19:03:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The Lustre 2.1 docs are incorrect, and will be fixed. In Lustre 2.x group_upcall has been replaced by identity_upcall (/proc/fs/lustre/mdt/${FSNAME}-MDT&lt;/p&gt;
{xxxx}
&lt;p&gt;/identity_upcall) You can set this with &apos;echo&apos; &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
